data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATON! Close to the #Bergen border on a quaint little cul-de-sac, this gem of a home in historic #Tappan inspires your imagination! NEW ROOF 2023 (complete tear-off with transferrable warranty). Other 2023 updates include front door, washer/dryer, dishwasher, and main sewer line snaked and videoed. Elec 200 AMP. Freshly painted thruout, fully fenced level backyard-all ready for you to enjoy!  SQ. FT DOES NOT INCLU THE FINISHED ATTIC (APPROX. 250 SQ.FT. ADDITIONAL)! Taxes are 2023 School $6,876+2023 Town/County $4,891.STAR rebate would apply for those who qualify. Ring camera system is excluded. Other house contents will remain as seen inclu shed with tools and maintenance supplies. Appliances are in working order at time of listing but sold strictly AS-IS, they will not be repaired or replaced at any point during the listing/contract. Inspection and appraisal for buyers info only. Trash collection is private, currently contracted with HIEP.
